sequenceDiagram
    actor C as Candidate
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI (App Runner)
    participant IN as Intake Agent
    participant MEM as Memory Agent
    participant ACM as AgentCore Memory
    participant PL as Planner Agent
    participant KB as Bedrock Knowledge Bases

    C->>FE: Upload resume + job description
    FE->>API: POST /session/start (Cognito auth)
    API->>IN: resume + JD text
    IN->>IN: Parse into IntakeProfile (strict JSON)
    IN-->>API: IntakeProfile
    API->>MEM: fetch MemoryProfile(candidateId)
    MEM->>ACM: read prior weaknesses + trend
    ACM-->>MEM: MemoryProfile (empty on first session)
    MEM-->>API: MemoryProfile
    API->>PL: IntakeProfile + MemoryProfile
    PL->>KB: retrieve rubrics + exemplars for target competencies
    KB-->>PL: grounding set
    PL->>PL: Generate fresh questions, weight weak areas higher
    PL-->>API: QuestionPlan
    API-->>FE: sessionId + QuestionPlan
    FE-->>C: Interview ready
